quran[26{c,v,t}:
69,9,aur iِssi Khat-tay azeem ka irtikaab firaon aur uss se pehlay ke logon ne aur tall patt ho jaane wali bustiyon ne kya
69,10,un sab ne apne rab ke rasool ki baat nah maani to uss ne unn ko barri sakhti ke sath pakra
69,11,jab pani ka tufaan hadd se guzar gaya to hum ne tum ko kashti mein sawaar kar diya tha
69,12,taakay iss waqea ko tumahray liye aik sabaq amooz yadgar bana den aur yaad rakhnay walay kaan is ki yaad mehfooz rakhen
69,13,phir jab aik dafaa soor mein phoonk maar di jaye gi
69,14,aur zameen aur pahoron ko utha kar aik hi chout mein rezah rezah kar diya jaye ga
69,15,uss roz woh honay wala waqea paish aa jaye ga
69,16,uss din aasman phatay ga aur is ki bandish dheeli par jaye gi
69,17,farishtay is ke atraaf o jawanib (kinaroow ) mein hon ge aur aath farishtay uss roz tairay rab ka arsh apne oopar uthaye hue hon ge
69,18,"woh din hoga jab tum log paish kiye jao ge, tumhara koi raaz bhi chhupa nah reh jaye ga"
69,19,"uss waqt jis ka nama aamaal uss ke seedhay haath mein diya jaye ga woh kahe ga"" lau dekho, parho mera nama aamaal"
69,20,"mein samjhta tha ke mujhe zaroor apna hisaab milnay wala hai """
69,21,pas woh dil pasand aish mein hoga
69,22,aliiiii maqam jannat mein
69,23,jis ke phalon ke guchay jhuke par rahay hon ge
69,24,( aisay logon se kaha jaye ga ) mazay se khao aur piyo apne unn aamaal ke badlay jo tum ne guzray hue dinon mein kiye hain
69,25,"aur jis ka nama aamaal uss ke baen haath mein diya jaye ga woh kahe ga"" kash mera aamaal nama mujhe nah diya gaya hota"
69,26,aur mein nah jaanta ke mera hisaab kya hai
69,27,kash meri wohi mout ( jo duniya mein aayi thi ) faisla kin hoti
69,28,aaj mera maal mere kuch kaam nah aaya
69,29,"mera sara Iqtidaar khatam ho gaya """
69,30,( hukum ho ga ) pakro isay aur iss ki gardan mein taoq daal do
69,31,phir isay jahannum mein jhonk do
69,32,phir iss ko sattar haath lambi zanjeer mein jakar do
69,33,yeh nah Allah buzurag o bartar par imaan lata tha
69,34,aur nah maskeen ko khana khilanay ki targheeb deta tha
